189
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:39,080
Your daughter's death has nothing to do with me.

190
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,480
No one can stop God from taking a life.

191
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,200
If you move again...

192
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:43,260
Move again, and I'll take you out too.

193
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,880
The match's name is Liu Jiang.

194
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:48,720
He used to be a doctor.

195
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,680
Made a lot of money selling health products.

196
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:52,360
In 2006, for illegal trading,

197
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,160
