239
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:20,080
It is me.

240
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,640
I can cure all diseases.

241
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:22,200
Trust me.

242
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,600
