271
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:34,480
You big guy!

272
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:35,200
You... Damn it.

273
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,160
I'll smash you!

274
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:39,560
Stop!

275
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:40,800
Liu Jiang!

276
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:41,480
Stop!

277
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,130
