278
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:53,400
Liu Jiang!

279
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,400
Liu Jiang!

280
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:03,560
Guard the door.

281
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,120
Stop chasing me!

282
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:21,640
Hurry up.

283
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:22,880
Hurry up.

284
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:24,640
Liu Jiang!

285
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:27,320
Liu Jiang!

286
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:33,800
Take the stairs.

287
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:34,280
Okay.

288
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:49,120
Here we go again.

289
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:50,780
Why are you always chasing me?

290
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:57,480
Stop chasing me.

291
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,120
My legs are going to break.

292
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,040
Liu Jiang, don't run.

293
00:13:59,040 --> 00:13:59,640
Stop chasing.

294
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,280
Why are you chasing me?

295
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,520
Stop chasing.

296
